3Z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"auto\"\u003eTo increase speed, deploy \u003ccode\u003eCode.gs\u003c/code\u003e multiple times to different Apps Script projects and use all their IDs:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"highlight highlight-source-json notranslate position-relative overflow-auto\" dir=\"auto\" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content=\"{\n  \u0026quot;script_ids\u0026quot;: [\n    \u0026quot;DEPLOYMENT_ID_1\u0026quot;,\n    \u0026quot;DEPLOYMENT_ID_2\u0026quot;,\n    \u0026quot;DEPLOYMENT_ID_3\u0026quot;\n  ]\n}\"\u003e\u003cpre\u003e{\n  \u003cspan class=\"pl-ent\"\u003e\"script_ids\"\u003c/span\u003e: [\n    \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-pds\"\u003e\"\u003c/span\u003eDEPLOYMENT_ID_1\u003cspan class=\"pl-pds\"\u003e\"\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e,\n    \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-pds\"\u003e\"\u003c/span\u003eDEPLOYMENT_ID_2\u003cspan class=\"pl-pds\"\u003e\"\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e,\n    \u003cspan class=\"pl-s\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"pl-pds\"\u003e\"\u003c/span\u003eDEPLOYMENT_ID_3\u003cspan class=\"pl-pds\"\u003e\"\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\n  ]\n}\u003c/pre\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cblockquote\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"auto\"\u003e\u003cg-emoji class=\"g-emoji\" alias=\"warning\"\u003e⚠️\u003c/g-emoji\u003e \u003cstrong\u003eNote:\u003c/strong\u003e If you are using multiple deployments, the auth-keys must be identical. (All deployments must use the same auth-key.)\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/blockquote\u003e\n\u003chr\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"markdown-heading\" dir=\"auto\"\u003e\u003ch2 tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"heading-element\" dir=\"auto\"\u003eUpdating the Google Relay\u003c/h2\u003e\u003ca id=\"user-content-updating-the-google-relay\" class=\"anchor\" aria-label=\"Permalink: Updating the Google Relay\" href=\"#updating-the-google-relay\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"octicon octicon-link\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"1