<p dir="auto">Firefox uses its own certificate store, so even after OS-level install you need to do this:</p>
<ol dir="auto">
<li>Go to <strong>Settings</strong> → <strong>Privacy &amp; Security</strong> → <strong>Certificates</strong> → <strong>View Certificates</strong>.</li>
<li>Go to the <strong>Authorities</strong> tab → click <strong>Import</strong>.</li>
<li>Select <code>ca/ca.crt</code> from the project folder.</li>
