<ul dir="auto">
<li><strong>Never share your <code>config.json</code></strong> — it has your password in it.</li>
<li><strong>Change the default <code>AUTH_KEY</code></strong> in <code>Code.gs</code> before deploying.</li>
<li><strong>Don't share the <code>ca/</code> folder</strong> — it contains your private certificate key.</li>
<li>Keep <code>listen_host</code> as <code>127.0.0.1</code> so only your computer can use the proxy.</li>
